{"tid":422337,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊game推薦]Day of Infamy","createTime":"2017-10-03T03:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T06:31:49.000Z","uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cba64bcee2f49d4024148a66725a0769023bcf5","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"呢隻game係由Insurgency間公司開發嘅二戰版,玩法同COD、OW、CS及Battlefield完全唔同,主打寫實及團隊合作。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講,一隊兵唔會出現全sniper或自動武器打天下嘅情況，反而類似神作red orchestra 果類作戰方式,士兵以Bolt action rifle為主打,要配合團隊合作進攻或防守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此game最特別之處就係radio system<br />\nOfficer可透過通訊兵call空襲同supply,團隊間嘅遠距語音交談亦要透過通訊兵傳達。<br />\n<br />\n加上遊戲主打寫實，生命並非以血量bar計,而是幾乎一槍必殺,所以CSGO嘅高手都未必覺得易玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，Day of Infamy以不少歷史上出名戰役作地圖，例如D day (dog red), Dunkirk,Rhineland及Crete等。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲以Wehrmacht, USA, Commonwealth三方勢力，希望鍾意WWII嘅ching可以一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ac7ec8bcb61293e6d20456318c05cdea2561e7","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/114113_eb8b92fd510c355c0ef5006fba2ea84e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F114113_eb8b92fd510c355c0ef5006fba2ea84e.jpg&h=d82cf18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12fb3dd6667c58a3a5fc401e70093c53677bec7","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"Steam will be featuring Day of Infamy in their free weekend promotion in the coming weeks! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1009ce859088150f159d5231de68d59d96b21bb","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"keep pushing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb60c0b78b1f5e57f68a9ed14661c35dac8b939","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>keep pushing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0c0dfa971d8d12c3fefbc9c57241f49c041541","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>keep pushing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9915551e2b4dd3301d699869daeba5aa22ea5a92","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>keep pushing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6fec3f01822db779f8dc6cba16dfad4be5845f","tid":422337,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=asUGhkLVlQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DasUGhkLVlQs&d=FvcdFaugKY56zwVCqh3gAnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=ddd75562\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=asUGhk